creative.title: K-Laser treatment in Ipoh!
creative.body:
K-Laser is a breakthrough treatment for joints and muscles - completely non-invasive, safe, and painless.

Unlike conventional treatments that may require injections or surgery, K-Laser is completely non-invasive. Using 4 advanced wavelengths of light, it penetrates deep into tissues to:
‚úÖ Reduce pain & swelling
‚úÖ Speed up healing of cartilage, muscles & ligaments
‚úÖ Improve blood flow for faster recovery

Perfect for patients with knee pain, as well as other joint conditions like shoulder, hip, or ankle issues.

‚ú® With Physiofit being the only centre in Ipoh with K-Laser Cube, patients here gain access to a cutting-edge therapy that helps them return to movement faster, safer, and with more confidence.

Contact us today to learn more!

üî• Dari zero terus jadi welding hero ‚Äî dalam satu minggu saja!

Di Master Weld Academy, kami percaya belajar mesti praktikal.
Minggu pertama pun sudah pegang tools sebenar, buat welding betul-betul, terus naik semangat!

Kalau kau mau tukar kerja, tambah skill, atau ikut minat ‚Äî sini la tempat mula.

üí¨PM saja kami untuk tanya jadual kelas & yuran.

Penat duduk ofis dari pagi sampai petang?
Kerja pejabat bukan untuk semua orang ‚Äî jangan risau, itu bukan salah pun.

Di dunia sebenar, kemahiran macam welding ni laku keras. Boleh buka banyak peluang kerja yang stabil, gaji ok, dan puas hati bila nampak hasil kerja tangan sendiri.

üìå Latihan 100% praktikal, terus pegang & buat
üìå Dapat sijil lepas habis kursus
üìå Ada peluang kerja lepas latihan
üìå Kemahiran real yang boleh pakai di mana-mana industri

Mau try? Kelas welding kami terbuka untuk semua.
Tiada pengalaman? Buli bah! Kami ajar dari basic.

Belajar terus dari cikgu yang memang ada pengalaman ‚Äî bukan setakat tunjuk, tapi betul-betul bawa masuk bengkel, buat sama-sama. Bila habis nanti, memang ready terus masuk kerja.

creative.title: Sumbangan dan Infaq
creative.body:
Yayasan Amanah percaya bahawa setiap individu berhak mendapat peluang kedua. Melalui Program Agrication, kami membuka pintu bagi Orang Bebas Berlesen (OBB) untuk kembali ke masyarakat dengan kemahiran baru.

Dengan memberikan latihan pertanian dan sokongan penuh, kami membantu mereka membina masa depan yang lebih cerah.

Sumbangan anda adalah salah satu usaha bagi  membolehkan kami menyediakan peralatan pertanian, benih berkualiti, serta akses pasaran bagi hasil tanaman mereka.

Marilah bersama-sama kita memberikan bantuan dan sokongan kepada mereka untuk kehidupan yang lebih baik.

Sumbangan boleh dibuat disini:
https://yayasanamanah.my/infaq/

#YayasanAmanah #Agrication #Parol #CSI #PBSL #Pertanian

campaign.name: Yayasan Amanah| Traffic Website | Client | Fyza | M1

creative.title: Sumbangan dan Infaq
creative.body:
Sumbangan anda telah memberikan sinar harapan kepada Orang Bebas Berlesen (OBB) yang bercita-cita untuk berjaya. Mereka, seperti individu lain, berhak untuk mencapai kejayaan.

Kesilapan yang pernah mereka lakukan bukan penghalang, malah boleh dijadikan sebagai pengajaran berharga untuk membina masa depan yang lebih baik.

Sumbangan anda bukan sekadar bantuan material, tetapi lebih daripada itu, ia menyalakan kembali semangat dan keyakinan mereka untuk meraih kehidupan yang lebih bermakna.

Ia membuktikan bahawa dengan sedikit bantuan dan sokongan daripada anda, seseorang yang pernah tersasar dapat bangkit kembali dan mencapai kejayaan.

Sumbangan boleh dibuat disini:
https://yayasanamanah.my/infaq/

creative.title: Infaq air mineral serendah RM2 disini.
creative.body:
Setitik air, setitik harapan. Setiap botol air mineral yang anda sumbangkan, membawa sinar harapan kepada mereka yang memerlukan.

Bayangkan keadaan mereka yang memerlukan air bersih untuk diminum, dahaga yang tak terpadamkan. Inilah realiti yang dihadapi oleh jutaan insan di luar sana. Mereka hidup tanpa akses kepada air bersih.

üå± Grow Your Own Lady's Fingers! üå±

*Q: What is the "Grow Your Own Food" contest all about?*  
*A:* It's a fun and educational contest where children aged 3 to 9 years old can learn to grow their own lady's fingers (okra). It's a wonderful way to introduce kids to gardening and healthy eating! üåø

*Q: Who can participate in this contest?*  
*A:* The contest is open to the public, specifically for children between the ages of 3 to 9 years old. üëßüë¶

*Q: How do we get started with growing lady's fingers?*  
*A:* First Step Kindergarten will provide all the necessary materials, including lady's finger seeds and soil. 

*Q: How can we share our progress in the contest?*  
*A:* We encourage participants to share photos and updates of their growing lady's fingers on our Facebook page. It's a fantastic way to inspire others and showcase your gardening skills! üì∏üå±

*Q: Is there a prize for the contest?*  
*A:* Yes! We will have exciting prizes for the best-grown lady's fingers. Call us for more details! üèÜüéâ

Terokai gaya hidup baru di Tujuh Residences!
Tujuh Residences merupakan tempat tinggal moden yang direka khas untuk seisi keluarga. 

Jenis A: 1 bilik & 1 bilik air (550 sq. ft.) 
Jenis B: 2 bilik & 2 bilik air (666 sq. ft.) 
Jenis C: 3 bilik & 2 bilik air (862 sq. ft.) 
Jenis D: Dual unit kunci | 2 bilik & 2 bilik air + 1 unit studio & 1 bilik air (909 sq. ft.) 

Tujuh Residences menawarkan nilai yang menarik dengan gabungan konsep elegan dengan harga mampu milik

‚úÖ Kolam renang, wading pool, BBQ pit. 
‚úÖ Tempat rehat: rumput hiasan, ruang membaca, bilik permainan, gazebo. 
‚úÖ Sukan: pool lounge chairs, garden step, yoga deck. 
‚úÖ Kekal sihat dengan peralatan gym yang disediakan
‚úÖ Dewan serbaguna untuk pelbagai jenis acara

Finding the perfect property takes time, but picking the right developer is key! Selecting the right real estate developer is important to ensure your needs are met in the long term.

Here are 4 things you should look out for:
1) The developer's background: Look for a developer with a proven track record, many past projects to review, and deep market knowledge. 
2) Quality of properties offered: Choose a developer known for using top materials and innovative building practices. Ô∏è
3) Problem solving skills: A good developer anticipates issues and guides you through a smooth buying journey.
4) Financial knowledge & expertise: Find a developer with strong financial partners, offering competitive options of properties.

At Avaland, we've been crafting communities and enhancing lives for generations. We use top-notch materials, solve problems proactively, and offer expert financial guidance ‚Äì all to make your home buying journey smooth and successful.

Schedule an appointment to discuss more!

creative.title: Sanderling LakeFront | Official Website
creative.body:
Buying your first home can be exciting, but also overwhelming! Here's a simple 5-step checklist to guide you on your journey:

1. Identify your reason: Investment or personal haven?
2. Check your credit score: A good score unlocks better loan options!
3. Plan your budget: Factor in loan amount, fees, and future maintenance costs.
4. Explore first-time buyer benefits: Government programs & tax breaks can help!
5. Find the perfect fit: Location, size, and features that match your needs and budget.
We offer a supportive environment, modern amenities, and a reputable developer ‚Äì all at an attractive price point, from only RM1,800/month. 

Get prepared to own your very first home! Register your interest today.

We at AxeHedge understand that investing has always been about managing and minimising risk. Choosing which platform to invest in is among those risks as well.

At AxeHedge, we understand this concern of yours and made our efforts to stand apart from the rest to ensure that you can invest with a peace of mind.

‚Ä¢ ùêìùêöùê¢ùê•ùê®ùê´ùêûùêù ùêüùê®ùê´ ùêëùêûùê≠ùêöùê¢ùê• ùêàùêßùêØùêûùê¨ùê≠ùê®ùê´ùê¨ üßµ‚Äì We at AxeHedge believe anyone can invest, given the right tools. That is why we ensured that our stock & fund options are tailored for retail investors like you! 
 
‚Ä¢ ùêÉùêöùê≠ùêö ùêÉùê´ùê¢ùêØùêûùêß ùêíùê≠ùê´ùêöùê≠ùêûùê†ùê¢ùêûùê¨ üìä ‚Äì At AxeHedge, we believe in providing transparency to ensure you make the right investing choice. That is why we provide data & information such as market recap and updated news on stocks worldwide.

‚Ä¢ ùêÅùêûùêßùêúùê°ùê¶ùêöùê´ùê§ùê¢ùêßùê† üéØ ‚Äì While our stocks are based on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE), we ensure our funds are also benchmarked against the likes of S&P 500, MSCI ACWI & more to ensure you‚Äôre getting maximum returns on your investments!
 
At AxeHedge, we invite you to invest smarter together üöÄDownload AxeHedge and start investing smarter today!

At AxeHedge, we cater our funds to be tailored just for you! 
 
We achieve this by ensuring our funds are:
 
‚Ä¢ ùêìùê´ùêÆùê•ùê≤ ùêÜùê•ùê®ùêõùêöùê• & ùêÉùê¢ùêØùêûùê´ùê¨ùê¢ùêüùê¢ùêûùêù üåè ‚Äì By ensuring our funds are not region specific & diversified across many different channels, we ensure that your risk is managed appropriately as well as increasing exposure towards many different assets.

‚Ä¢ ùêéùê©ùê≠ùê¢ùê¶ùê¢ùê¨ùêûùêù ùêëùê¢ùê¨ùê§ ‚Äì ùêëùêûùê∞ùêöùê´ùêù üìà ‚Äì By optimising our investment strategies, we aim to strike a balance between generating returns for our users as well as managing any potential risks.

‚Ä¢ ùêÇùê®ùêßùê¨ùê¢ùê¨ùê≠ùêûùêßùê≠ ùêåùê¢ùêù ‚Äì ùê≠ùê® ‚Äì ùêãùê®ùêßùê† ùêëùêöùêßùê†ùêû ùêéùêÆùê≠ùê©ùêûùê´ùêüùê®ùê´ùê¶ùêöùêßùêúùêû üí™üèª ‚Äì We at AxeHedge aim to ensure our funds consistently outperform benchmarks over a mid-to-long term investment horizon to ensure we can maximise returns for our users.

At AxeHedge, we invite you to invest smarter together üöÄ Download AxeHedge and start investing smarter today!

Investing may seem scary for beginners üò±But don‚Äôt worry as your can always start with funds!

Funds are an easier option for investing for amateur investors as they have many solid reasons to start investing in them first. Among them are: 
 
‚Ä¢ ùêÉùê¢ùêØùêûùê´ùê¨ùê¢ùêüùê¢ùêúùêöùê≠ùê¢ùê®ùêß ‚Äì Among the key reasons to start investing in funds is diversification. Just by starting to invest in a single fund, you will be exposed to variety of assets from various industries & sectors.
